compbench (2.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Rewrite in C with direct kernel interface measurements.
  * Removed dependencies: python3, python3-psutil, pv, btrfs-compsize.
  * Compression ratio via statvfs, CPU via /proc/stat, disk I/O via sysfs.
  * Data copy via copy_file_range() syscall.
  * CLI redesigned: --zstd MIN-MAX range, --no-integrity-check, etc.

